{
  "text": "We have tried dealing with the diamond crystal. We have tried both using the crystal around my neck and then dangling it from a chain under my right hand. I think that possibly to put the best word only wrist, I should dangle the crystal just below my right hand, a distance of just a centimeter or two, only directly above the wrist. Is this correct? I am wrong. This would be appropriate if you were practised at your healing art to work with a powerful crystal such as you have, while unable to perceive the magnetic flux of the subtle bodies is perhaps the same as recommending that the beginner with saw and nail create the Vatican. There is great art in the use of the swung crystal. At this point in your development, you would do well to work with the unpowerful crystals in ascertaining not only the physical major energy centers, but also the physical secondary and tertiary energy centers, and then begin to find the corresponding subtle body energy centers. In this way, you may activate your own inner vision.",
